Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.57,0:00:06.93,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.19,0:00:09.17,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,莫名其妙地就倒下了  吓了我一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.51,0:00:12.15,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,突然眼前一黑  脚一软…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.27,0:00:13.99,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  让你担心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.90,0:00:16.46,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,轻度贫血吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.56,0:00:18.12,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办  去医院吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.26,0:00:19.33,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,不  没事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.45,0:00:21.31,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,我想休息一下就会好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.85,0:00:24.58,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,补习已经开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.22,0:00:28.05,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,一天不去也没什么大的影响吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.30,0:00:29.24,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,今天就休息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.33,0:00:29.80,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.33,0:00:31.97,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,往人不去打工吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.04,0:00:33.17,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,今天不去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.51,0:00:40.61,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,与往人一起去了学校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.96,0:00:42.73,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,与往人一起玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.90,0:00:46.16,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,知了撞进了往人的早饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.40,0:00:48.47,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,与往人一起去了车站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.70,0:00:50.62,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,与往人一起去了神社
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.46,0:00:54.20,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以看人家的日记
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.00,0:00:57.16,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,你就不会写点别的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.70,0:01:00.10,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵  我觉得写得满好的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.52,0:01:04.27,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,听好  说实话你没有写日记的天赋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.58,0:01:07.89,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,所以今后不要总写做过的事  要写想要做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.00,0:01:10.05,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,可是  那样就不是日记
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.10,0:01:11.39,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,不  是日记
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.67,0:01:14.42,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我会实现你写的所有的愿望的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.25,0:01:18.34,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,好想去海边啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.92,0:01:20.10,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,与往人一起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.07,0:01:23.80,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,还没和你一起到过沙滩呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.36,0:01:27.79,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,在那里挖沙子啦  捡漂亮的贝壳啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.37,0:01:31.68,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,我说  你不是每天都能看到海么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.51,0:01:33.26,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,嘎哦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.82,0:01:34.45,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,好疼～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.89,0:01:35.70,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.17,0:01:40.04,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,陪你去海边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.37,0:01:42.93,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.11,0:03:27.06,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子说想要去海边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.70,0:03:30.31,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,但我却没能带她去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.03,0:03:41.87,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,观铃病倒了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.22,0:03:44.97,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  一整天了都没好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.29,0:03:46.42,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,正在房间里休息呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.57,0:03:47.83,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,你去看看她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.56,0:03:52.68,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,让她看到我这幅醉样  病情就变得更糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.78,0:03:54.65,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,先不管她  看我买了寿司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.80,0:03:56.73,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,咱们来高兴高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.64,0:04:03.98,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…  你刚才的举动极大地伤害了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.28,0:04:06.50,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要收养观铃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.83,0:04:07.39,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.78,0:04:10.11,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么收养了观铃！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.53,0:04:13.21,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  原来她对你讲了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.40,0:04:18.22,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,不是收养  是别人硬塞给我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.73,0:04:21.00,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我说了不愿意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.06,0:04:23.93,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,正因如此  她才无法向你撒娇吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.11,0:04:27.12,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,有点负责感好不好！  你可是她唯一的亲人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.71,0:04:30.86,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子要和谁变得亲近时就会发作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.94,0:04:34.10,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,我和那孩子之间保持着一定的距离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.66,0:04:36.41,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,因此才能生活在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.23,0:04:38.66,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,根本不像一对母女是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.06,0:04:41.66,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也不是她真正的母亲  所以什么也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.45,0:04:45.39,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,真难吃  买错东西了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.24,0:04:55.87,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,女孩在做梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.53,0:04:58.57,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,最初是个天空的梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.14,0:05:01.50,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,梦渐渐地追溯着过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.55,0:05:05.52,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个梦在侵蚀着女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.50,0:05:09.00,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,渐渐地  她会开始感觉到本不该有的痛楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.62,0:05:12.65,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,不久  女孩将会忘记一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.48,0:05:17.77,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至连自己最亲近的人都忘掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.98,0:05:21.27,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,然后在做完最后一场梦的早晨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.84,0:05:23.50,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,女孩会死去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.97,0:05:26.86,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子一直孤零零的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.89,0:05:31.26,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,因为两个人的心靠近的话  两个人都会病倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.79,0:05:33.26,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,两个人都无法得救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.20,0:05:35.64,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,所以那个女孩说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.29,0:05:37.90,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,「离开我…」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.44,0:05:41.90,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,她是个善良并且坚强的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.34,0:05:44.26,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,也正因此我才能活了下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.31,0:05:46.74,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,但是  那孩子却…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.88,0:05:51.90,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,在这片天空中  有一个拥有一双翅膀的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.73,0:05:56.36,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,她总是孤零零的一个人  长不大就消逝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.94,0:05:59.16,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,一个人重复着那个悲伤的梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.32,0:06:05.47,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,去旅行！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.73,0:06:07.26,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,对  一个人悠然地去旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.34,0:06:08.53,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,温泉之旅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.40,0:06:11.28,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在想什么！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.40,0:06:13.54,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,她…  观铃怎么办！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.84,0:06:15.15,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,交给你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.24,0:06:18.57,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,别太接近她的话  也就不会发作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.77,0:06:20.48,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.27,0:06:23.04,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,观铃正在做着一个梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.35,0:06:25.94,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个梦把观铃弄成这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.29,0:06:26.84,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.26,0:06:29.99,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,我想起了妈妈说过的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.58,0:06:33.71,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,我妈妈以前也遇到过这种病状的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.16,0:06:35.83,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,再过不久  观铃会忘记一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.93,0:06:37.63,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,忘记我  也忘记你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.26,0:06:40.76,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,然后在做完最后一场梦的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.90,0:06:42.93,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,观铃  可能会死去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.96,0:06:48.54,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,我说  开玩笑也得分轻重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.67,0:06:50.94,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是玩笑  观铃她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.96,0:06:51.59,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,躲开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.33,0:06:52.81,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.18,0:06:57.78,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,我进来了哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.86,0:07:01.36,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  醒着呢吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.76,0:07:04.24,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  刚醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.90,0:07:06.87,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,我听到了妈妈的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.15,0:07:09.83,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  说是出去一段时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.18,0:07:11.17,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.97,0:07:16.74,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,我非常喜欢妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.96,0:07:23.06,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,去海边吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.09,0:07:32.32,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢走  不用勉强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.68,0:07:33.19,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.10,0:07:36.47,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是乌鸦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.76,0:07:41.35,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,观铃！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.78,0:07:44.20,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  没关系吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.31,0:07:44.79,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.10,0:07:47.06,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.71,0:07:50.24,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,V～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.52,0:07:53.65,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,明明每天都走过这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.03,0:07:56.49,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,海有这么遥远吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.72,0:08:02.30,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.58,0:08:07.30,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.66,0:08:12.19,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,我又…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.16,0:08:14.44,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,又要发作吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.72,0:08:15.53,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.50,0:08:19.71,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,一会儿就会好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.48,0:08:23.28,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,海…  明天再去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.00,0:08:31.76,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,平静下来了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.51,0:08:32.97,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.21,0:08:35.64,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,呐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.90,0:08:38.71,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚我又做梦了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.08,0:08:41.11,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,这回是个快乐的梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.57,0:08:43.89,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是黑夜但天空很亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.57,0:08:46.76,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,我想那一定是节日祭奠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.37,0:08:49.40,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,我就那样在远处眺望着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.07,0:08:50.65,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.45,0:08:52.44,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,往人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.77,0:08:53.37,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.53,0:08:56.57,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,往人正在寻找的那个人和我的梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.81,0:08:58.39,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,是相互联系的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.69,0:09:01.13,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢  应该不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.05,0:09:07.04,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,我思考了很多后得出一个结论
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.12,0:09:08.28,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,愿意听我说吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.92,0:09:11.95,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,我的梦代表着另外的那个我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.44,0:09:15.48,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,现在  那个孩子正在痛苦着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.16,0:09:18.43,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,我要努力地做梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.23,0:09:22.39,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,因为多做些梦  也许就会明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.23,0:09:27.24,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,这样  也许就能够帮助那个孩子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.51,0:09:33.05,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,往人  我开始做这个梦并不是偶然的对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.55,0:09:36.59,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,我认为今年的夏天是不同寻常的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.93,0:09:39.24,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,我想努力去交朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.78,0:09:42.82,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,于是便遇到了往人  然后开始做梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.24,0:09:45.45,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,这一切一定都是相互联系的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.42,0:09:48.47,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,所以  我想努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.85,0:09:51.57,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,想把这个夏天作为自己最美的回忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.77,0:09:53.87,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是和往人相遇的夏天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.05,0:09:58.66,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.86,0:10:01.76,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.99,0:10:03.67,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉舒服多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.70,0:10:09.28,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,哇！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.00,0:10:10.59,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,观铃！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.11,0:10:14.25,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  这是怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.14,0:10:16.69,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,脚无法动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.28,0:10:30.59,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,还是把圣叫来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.07,0:10:32.63,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,要不去大的医院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.39,0:10:37.02,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,不  医生肯定是治不好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.57,0:10:40.09,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,其实往人也是知道的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.90,0:10:44.40,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,就是我做的那个梦把我弄成这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.65,0:10:45.43,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.03,0:10:47.76,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天晚上我又做梦了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.20,0:10:49.35,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,是一个旅途的梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.81,0:10:50.40,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,旅途？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.82,0:10:52.35,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,寻找什么东西的旅途
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.85,0:10:55.96,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,我在森林中走了好多天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.51,0:10:58.42,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很累  但我努力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.89,0:11:01.32,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,因为有喜欢的人陪在我身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.42,0:11:02.51,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢的人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.90,0:11:04.11,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,我自己明白的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.27,0:11:07.91,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,我每做一次梦  就会变得衰弱一些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.27,0:11:10.99,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,最终一定会像天空中的少女那样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.01,0:11:12.63,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,别说傻话！  怎么可能！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.91,0:11:15.10,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵  往人生气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.57,0:11:18.32,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,不要去想什么另外的那个你的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.59,0:11:19.99,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,先把病养好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.90,0:11:23.19,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  观铃是坚强的孩子！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.41,0:11:50.19,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,往人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.34,0:11:52.05,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,往人！  往人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.93,0:11:54.86,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.55,0:11:56.85,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,没事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.18,0:12:00.02,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的话就不会那副表情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.76,0:12:02.64,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,我原本就是这副表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.81,0:12:04.29,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,观铃  回床上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.40,0:12:06.18,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能不管往人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.37,0:12:09.34,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,我说了没事了  不要太让我操心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.01,0:12:10.54,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.66,0:12:22.33,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,这痕迹是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.13,0:12:29.12,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,好疼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.64,0:12:31.05,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,观铃  振作点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.83,0:12:35.57,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,观铃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.80,0:12:45.73,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的  一会就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.12,0:12:47.35,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,陪着我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.40,0:12:49.03,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我在你身边的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.44,0:12:51.92,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  陪着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.99,0:12:59.66,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么大家只把我留下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.91,0:13:06.17,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.83,0:13:07.80,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,现在没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.90,0:13:09.00,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,往人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.28,0:13:10.60,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,我什么事都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.17,0:13:13.19,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办  还是叫圣来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.64,0:13:14.31,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,或是叫佳乃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.51,0:13:16.80,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,美风已经离开小镇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.90,0:13:17.96,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,要不叫个同学来…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.05,0:13:20.95,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  我不想给别人添麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.20,0:13:24.01,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,别说瞎话  你很想交朋友吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.11,0:13:25.24,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,不喜欢一个人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.11,0:13:27.54,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,往人在就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.76,0:13:30.57,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,有往人陪着我  其他的什么都不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.21,0:13:32.20,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,会不会给你添麻烦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.63,0:13:33.25,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.01,0:13:38.61,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,好想和往人一起去海边啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.75,0:13:40.20,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,在沙滩上玩耍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.49,0:13:43.36,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,追逐跑啦  打水仗啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.57,0:13:46.03,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,最后大家挥手道别
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.16,0:13:48.61,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,不过现在我先忍着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.99,0:13:52.62,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,这样到时候真去的时候会更高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.04,0:13:54.62,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,观铃加油～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.58,0:13:56.34,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.37,0:13:57.99,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,观铃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.08,0:13:58.64,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.89,0:14:00.51,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得差不多该离开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.29,0:14:08.36,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,再这样下去的话  我俩都会病倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.98,0:14:11.71,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我决定逃离这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.16,0:14:15.82,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,离开这个小镇  去一个再也不会见到你的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.11,0:14:16.94,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,一个人…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.38,0:14:17.95,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.62,0:14:21.46,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,我们靠得太近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.35,0:14:27.12,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,那就…  没办法了是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.76,0:14:29.12,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.08,0:14:33.57,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,我就说嘛  一直一个人玩的话就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.38,0:14:35.13,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,也许吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.06,0:14:39.73,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,这个暑假过的很高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.11,0:14:42.27,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,和往人一起度过的这个暑假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.40,0:14:45.23,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.67,0:14:46.36,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.70,0:14:47.18,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.07,0:14:51.68,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,已经没车了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.08,0:14:54.20,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,往人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.81,0:14:59.68,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…  今早的梦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.94,0:15:02.23,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人被孤零零地关了起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.33,0:15:03.35,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,很寂寞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.57,0:15:07.72,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,一直在等着谁来带我出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.96,0:15:12.11,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我也想和往人一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.42,0:15:14.61,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,不能带我一起去吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.25,0:15:17.96,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是想离开这个家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.29,0:15:20.33,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,是必须要离开你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.18,0:15:24.41,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,只要我不在了  你的病应该可以治好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.95,0:15:28.30,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,所以  我是无法陪在你身边的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.35,0:15:29.18,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.33,0:15:30.66,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.92,0:15:33.67,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  又说了傻话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.12,0:15:34.62,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.10,0:15:40.23,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,那再见了…  保重身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.44,0:15:42.05,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,你也要加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.38,0:15:43.95,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,一个人也要加油啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.29,0:15:46.15,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  一个人也要加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.45,0:15:47.80,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,我是坚强的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.12,0:15:50.10,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,好  再见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.53,0:15:58.28,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,观铃…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.71,0:16:26.16,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,往人现在在想什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.38,0:16:28.86,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,有没有想着要让看的人欢笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.37,0:16:31.08,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,不这样的话是无法操动人偶的哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.50,0:16:33.46,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,不能只想着要让人偶动起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.63,0:16:37.00,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,要想着为什么要让人偶动起来  这样人偶就会动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.28,0:16:44.38,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,做的不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.63,0:16:50.54,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子说想去海边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.27,0:16:53.79,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,但我却没能带她去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.49,0:16:57.82,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,往人  这回你一定要救她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.78,0:17:00.48,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,在这个人偶里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.81,0:17:03.36,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,聚集着未能实现的愿望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.98,0:17:08.87,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,我的母亲  祖母等在身体衰弱前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.04,0:17:11.52,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,都把自己的力量封印在了这个人偶里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.22,0:17:15.33,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,为了有一天有个人可以实现这个愿望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.34,0:17:19.94,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,所以  我也会变成愿望中的一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.70,0:17:23.23,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,如何使用这个人偶是你的自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.81,0:17:27.19,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,就算忘记天空中那个女孩也没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.56,0:17:29.59,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,但是往人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.63,0:17:33.82,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,在某个小镇上  你一定会和那个女孩相遇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.97,0:17:37.76,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你无论如何都想救那个女孩的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.20,0:17:40.31,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,就心念这个人偶吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.13,0:17:43.88,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我会和你在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.92,0:17:49.23,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,心念这个人偶…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.84,0:17:54.30,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,这个大哥哥一直怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.11,0:17:58.67,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,天热中暑了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.18,0:18:04.28,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,放开我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.79,0:18:08.12,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了  帮帮我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.25,0:18:12.37,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,看这个  告诉我如何做才能变的有意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.44,0:18:14.87,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,如何做才能让别人欢笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.13,0:18:16.46,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.50,0:18:17.63,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,不可思议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.78,0:18:20.18,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,不过没什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.96,0:18:25.34,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,别光是走  让它再表演些其他的如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.14,0:18:28.23,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,比如装成说话的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.33,0:18:31.80,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,表演段舞蹈如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.12,0:18:33.41,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,舞…舞蹈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.50,0:18:37.21,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,要更用心些才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.07,0:18:57.51,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的表演非常有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.58,0:18:59.57,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,既有趣  又可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.80,0:19:00.34,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.45,0:19:02.59,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢啦  一直陪着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.40,0:19:05.57,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,那就加油吧  大哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.76,0:19:06.55,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.82,0:19:25.74,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,观铃  我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.22,0:19:28.52,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,哪里都不去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.02,0:19:31.65,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,陪在你身边  让你一直欢笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.40,0:19:33.46,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,往人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.80,0:19:35.08,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,我找到窍门了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.23,0:19:36.98,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,这回的表演一定很有趣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.18,0:19:38.74,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你要仔细看哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.15,0:19:43.72,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,观铃！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.19,0:19:48.05,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,观铃！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.34,0:19:50.37,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,你看啊！ 你笑啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.64,0:19:59.58,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我一直都没注意到呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.21,0:20:01.66,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,陪在你的身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.05,0:20:05.82,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,看着你的笑容就是我要追求的幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.08,0:20:08.37,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我要追求的幸福啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.32,0:20:10.47,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,我哪里都不会去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.33,0:20:12.67,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,在我的身边欢笑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.38,0:20:15.47,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,呐…  观铃…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.14,0:20:22.90,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,往人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.38,0:20:25.05,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在一定要想起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.38,0:20:26.92,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,自己必须做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.57,0:20:31.67,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,我… 我想陪在观铃身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.24,0:20:35.14,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话  想从与她相遇的时候起重新来过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.84,0:20:37.18,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,这回一定…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.76,0:20:39.64,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,永远陪在观铃身边…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.06,0:20:49.32,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.78,0:20:52.16,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,本以为无法再起来了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.33,0:20:54.09,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,往人…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.85,0:20:56.14,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.65,0:20:58.61,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,你回来看我了是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.23,0:21:02.30,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,你看  我又恢复健康了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.86,0:21:04.69,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,我还可以加油啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.89,0:21:06.44,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,呐…  往人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.96,0:21:24.96,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,好疼──
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.85,0:21:28.82,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,你为何在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.68,0:21:31.97,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,有空说话的话赶快给我起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.51,0:21:34.63,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,没见过你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.10,0:21:38.37,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,正八位下左卫门大志 柳也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.13,0:21:41.73,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,你是从哪里掉下来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.09,0:21:44.00,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道我的名字吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.25,0:21:46.40,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  咱们才刚刚见面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.48,0:21:48.52,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.95,0:21:51.16,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然还有人不知道我呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.94,0:21:52.70,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,神奈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.09,0:21:54.64,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,那可真是巧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.81,0:21:57.71,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,我奉命要保护的翼人的名字也是神奈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.83,0:21:59.81,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,哦～　真的是很巧呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.93,0:22:04.11,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,就是说嘛  哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.06,0:22:07.08,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,蠢材！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.78,0:23:46.52,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,说到翼人  是神的使者吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.02,0:23:50.76,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,当遇到饥荒和疫病时  祈祷神的力量来保护大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.92,0:23:53.64,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,是可以直接和神对话的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.94,0:23:59.28,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,所谓家族  就是大家聚在一起生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.76,0:24:02.87,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,好想见妈妈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.68,0:24:07.02,Context,,0000,0000,0000,,没有比见不到母亲更残酷的事了
